Package com.ecommerceservice.service

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AdminService
    admin service, can add customer, update customer, signup admin, signin admin, delete admin by adminId, get admin by name and phone
    CustomerService
    customer service, can signup customer, login customer, delete product from cart, add product to cart, checkout, get customer by customerid
    OrderService
    Order service, can save order, get order by orderId, get orders by customerId
    StorageAdminService
    storage admin service, can signup storage admin, signin storage admin, delete storage admin by id, get storage admin by name and phone, add storage
    StorageService
    storage service, can add storage, delete storage, check storage, show all storage
